- Smoke Editing-> generate setter/getter
- switch to Show Source of Selected Element Only
- select fName in Outliner
- add field private int fCount;

- generate Setter & Getter
- select generated Setter, Getter and field in outliner
- activate delete, press OK

1. Open TestCase.java
2. switch to segmented view
3. select fName, its getter and its setter in the Outline view
4. delete them (via Outline view)
